@startuml deleteComment
!include ../../theme/theme-dark-seq.puml
title deleteComment flow
actor User
participant Resolver
participant CommentsService as C
participant LikesService as L
database DB

User -> Resolver: deleteComment()
Resolver -> C: deleteComment() : bool

group commentsRepo.manager.transaction
  C -> DB: lockEntityByIdOrThrow(Comment) + load user relation
  DB --> C: comment

  C -> C: validate ownership

  C -> L: deleteLikes()
  L -> DB: repo.delete()
  DB --> L: ok
  L --> C: ok

  C -> DB: manager.remove(Comment)
  DB -> DB: CASCADE delete comment activities
  DB --> C: comment deleted
end

C --> Resolver: true
Resolver --> User: data.deleteComment = true

== Error rule ==
note over C,DB
If any awaited step inside the transaction throws:
TypeORM issues ROLLBACK, then error bubbles to resolver,
and resolver returns a GraphQL error.
end note
@enduml
